## Implementation Plan: better-auth with SurrealDB v2

### Overview

This plan integrates [better-auth](https://better-auth.com/docs/installation) with the existing Bun.serve() server using a custom SurrealDB v2 adapter built with [`createAdapterFactory`](https://better-auth.com/docs/guides/create-a-db-adapter). The community adapter ([Necmttn/surrealdb-better-auth](https://github.com/Necmttn/surrealdb-better-auth)) pins SDK v1 and creates its own connection; this adapter shares the project's existing `Surreal` instance and uses parameterized queries instead of string interpolation.

